from adam bellini berkeley edu adam schwartz subject re seventh centuri armenian math problem nntp post host bellini berkeley edu organ berkeley erl line in articl qn innd flop engr orst edu koc rize ece orst edu cetin kaya koc write problem my father told follow stori dure famou war armenian persian princ zaurak kamsarakan perform extraordinari heroic deed three time singl month attack persian troop the first time struck half persian armi the second time pursu persian slaughter one fourth soldier the third time destroy one eleventh persian armi the persian still aliv number two hundr eighti fled nakhichevan and so remaind find mani persian soldier massacr answer thought implic princ destroy one fourth the remain persian troop second round remain on third round thi would mean answer